dc_title_s: A new and correct map of the world: laid down according to the newest discoveries and from the most exact observations; by Herman Moll, geographer. To his Royal Highness, George, Prince of Denmark, Lord High Admiral, Great Britain and Ireland.
dc_description_s: Relief shown pictorially. Includes images of the planets, sun and moon. 1 map: hand col.; 48 x 95 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
